title: Fictional Women Around the World: Ahsoka Tano
itunes:title: Fictional Women Around the World: Ahsoka Tano
description:
Once Anakin Skywalker's padawan, Ahsoka Tano walked away from the Jedi Order to become a prominent spy in the Rebellion. We trace the story of how she went from a despised character to a beloved one, and what her future might hold.
